          "value": "gpt-4o-mini"
        },
        "messages": {
          "values": [
            {
              "content": "=\"=You are a CRM data extractor. Extract ONLY the mentioned fields from the transcription.\n\nText: {{ $('Transcribe Audio').item.json.text }}\n\nALLOWED FIELDS: {{ $('Parse Fields').item.json.fields.map(f => f.name + ' (' + f.label + ')').join(', ') }}\n\nRULES:\n- Use ONLY the field names provided in ALLOWED FIELDS.\n- Do NOT use the \"name\" field for the deal itself.\n- If the user mentions tasks to be done, extract them into a \"tasks\" array. Each task should have a \"title\" and an optional \"description\".\n- If the user mentions notes to be taken, extract them into a \"notes\" array. Each note should have a \"title\" and \"content\".\n- If no tasks are mentioned, do not include the \"tasks\" key in the output.\n- If no notes are mentioned, do not include the \"notes\" key in the output.\n- Output a single JSON object. Deal fields should be top-level properties.\n- Output ONLY JSON.\n\nExamples:\n- Deal with both tasks and notes:\n  {\n    \"title\": \"ACME Corp Deal\",\n    \"deal_value\": 10000,\n    \"tasks\": [\n      { \"title\": \"Send proposal\", \"description\": \"Draft and send the proposal by Friday\" },\n      { \"title\": \"Schedule follow-up call\" }\n    ],\n    \"notes\": [\n      { \"title\": \"Initial Meeting\", \"content\": \"Client is interested in product X and Y. They mentioned a budget around $10k.\" }\n    ]\n  }\n- Deal with only tasks:\n  {\n    \"title\": \"ACME Corp Deal\",\n    \"deal_value\": 10000,\n    \"tasks\": [\n      { \"title\": \"Send proposal\", \"description\": \"Draft and send the proposal by Friday\" }\n    ]\n  }\n- Deal with only notes:\n  {\n    \"title\": \"ACME Corp Deal\",\n    \"deal_value\": 10000,\n    \"notes\": [\n      { \"title\": \"Initial Meeting\", \"content\": \"Client is interested in product X and Y.\" }\n    ]\n  }\n- Deal with neither:\n  {\n    \"title\": \"ACME Corp Deal\",\n    \"deal_value\": 10000\n  }\n\""
            }
          ]
        },
